  { q: "For academic writing, your sources should be:", options: ["Mostly internet", "Primarily scholarly and peer-reviewed, supplemented by credible sources", "Only books", "Any source"], answer: 1, explanation: "Academic writing should rely primarily on peer-reviewed and scholarly sources with supporting credible materials." }
